  "2262820": {
    "name": "永生之庭",
    "steam_appid": 2262820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/edab86d23a9c09f43df4519e5da4960f.avif?t=1768886018\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里是「学园」，一所瀰漫着黑色雾气的怪异校园，<strong>而你</strong>，失去所有记忆的你，将成为这所校园中唯一的教师，并与四名学生一同生活，并逃离这所由黑雾砌成的牢笼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/09731cffeef8fd93264f8c04c8e72725.avif?t=1768886018\" width=600 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可攻略的敌方引导者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，以「扩散黑雾」为己任的「引导者」们会向你和学生们发起进攻，当然，你可以在战斗中击溃她们</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过...你也可以选择提升她们的好感度，或许能与这些引导者发展更深入的关系?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/52cd5aada876e9fe3c7a895b0e8e8e28.avif?t=1768886018\" width=600 height=350 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >十位以上的可攻略对象</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/203963237b7290a08ca6508fa73ea1e0.avif?t=1768886018\" width=600 height=350 /></span>永生之庭中，可攻略对象多达十二位(...或许还有更多...?) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你喜欢的角色成为恋人吧! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创新的战斗系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构筑你的队伍，带着「唤醒者」们驱散垄罩校园的黑雾吧! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/788e75760300bd91a9ccb00bd4085f77.poster.avif?t=1768886018\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/788e75760300bd91a9ccb00bd4085f77.webm?t=1768886018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/788e75760300bd91a9ccb00bd4085f77.mp4?t=1768886018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >如果只想看剧情呢?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在永生之庭中，有多种难度可供玩家选择!(也可以自定义难度) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果真的不想游玩战斗的部份，也可以在游戏中取得极为强力(破坏平衡)的道具以快速通关喔!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗以外，是属于你的日常</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了战斗以外，你还可以经营自已的教室，并与学生们互动 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着好感度越来越高...学生们也许...?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/63d7e9b8e2758707acdfde590bde7c1d.avif?t=1768886018\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras_big/63d7e9b8e2758707acdfde590bde7c1d.avif?t=1768886018 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >和学生间的关系更加紧密...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着与学生间的好感度提升，除了能解锁好感度剧情外，也能见到学生的另一面。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但老师，请务必注意，<strong>如果过份偏袒某个学生...</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可能会导致发生一些...糟糕的事情? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >找回记忆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着主线剧情推进，你会渐渐找回自己曾经的记忆，以及这所学校存在的<strong>意义</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >五十个以上的可使用角色!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在永生之庭中，一共有五十个以上风格各异的角色，且每个角色都有四个技能可用 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/172ce4b9c0e575af0025df6b640d0689.avif?t=1768886018\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >总觉得很熟悉的抽卡系统?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着回合数推进，你能获得越来越多的「唤醒券」，这些唤醒券可以用来召唤「唤醒者」们 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觉得很熟悉?没错!这就是揉合了当前热门手游的抽卡系统! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了经典的十连抽以外，天井、兑换等机制也能在游戏里找到! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏内的抽卡无须(也不能)通过内购系统获得，想获得更多抽卡券，请升级你的教室建筑</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果已经厌倦了抽卡，也能开启某个特殊的系统...蓝绿修改器!(这将会导致无法完成某些成就) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在开启蓝绿修改器之后，可以通过「伪课金」来获得大量的抽卡券! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >数十个风格各异的敌方Boss</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永生之庭，除了有着大篇幅主线的「引导者」外，还有不少特殊Boss </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个Boss背后都有属于自己的一段故事，当然，也有着各式各样不同的战斗方式 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/35f3f97a1b3e54c2992e2b89aa8417fc.avif?t=1768886018\" width=612 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(虽然游戏中出现前作的角色，但请放心，本游戏中不存在任何意义/层面上的NTR要素) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(若有任何疑虑可以在BiliBili私信与我讨论) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超简单的创意工房系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你想将自己的角色做入游戏中? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希望也能拥有自己的唤醒者? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用角色建立工具，即便没有编写模块的经验，也能短时间做出一个自己的角色! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无内购系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不少玩家一直关心永生之庭中会不会存在内购系统(是不是有课金?) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在此请大家放心!永生之庭中不存在任何的内购(课金)系统! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请放心游玩噢!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/a40f750a5a0f54e95c0183381604482f.avif?t=1768886018\" width=600 height=400 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262820/extras/f72a6f56355c86baf62cdbc6486b22ad.avif?t=1768886018\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p>",
